name: History Fighter - The historical figure fight club!
blurb: Historical Figures transformed into comic Superheroes and Villains YOU collect and battle with in story and multiplayer game modes!

rewards.reward: :: The Supporter :: You'll get our DIGITAL REWARDS KIT which includes an illustrated character eBook and game guide plus exclusive wallpaper, original music and poetry from the game team, and a printable History Fighter coloring book! You will be listed as a Model Citizen in the game credits.

:: The Fan :: You'll get the Digital Rewards Kit (above) PLUS a commemorative print featuring a History Fighter character to be determined by a vote (those who pledge this tier vote on it) and SIGNED BY THE GAME TEAM. You will be listed as a Cadet in the game credits.

:: The Player :: You'll get the Digital Rewards Kit PLUS access to our Beta test, PLUS a special BACKERS-ONLY BOOSTER PACK that includes a LIMITED GAME CARD, the FEMME FATALE PACK, and special BACKER AVATAR when the game goes live! You will be listed as a Field Agent in the game credits.

:: The Collector :: You'll get the Digital Rewards Kit and Backers-Only Booster Pack PLUS a first-edition deck of History Fighter as a PHYSICAL CARD GAME, a true collector's item signed by the game's creators! PLUS access to our Beta test and you will be listed as a Special Agent in the game credits.

:: THE KEYMASTER :: You'll get the Digital Rewards Kit PLUS access to our Beta test, PLUS the Backers-Only Booster Pack PLUS all Episodes for SEASON 01 UNLOCKED! You will be listed as a Special Agent in the game credits.

:: The Fashionista :: You'll get the Digital Rewards Kit and Backers-Only Booster Pack PLUS an official Team History Fighter T-SHIRT. (this tier does not include the physical deck or Season 01 Unlocked) You will have access to our Beta test, and you will be listed as a Secret Agent in the game credits.

:: The Collaborator :: WELCOME TO THE TEAM :: You'll get ALL DIGITAL REWARDS including the Digital Rewards Kit, Backers-Only Booster Pack, Season 01 Fully Unlocked, PLUS access to our Beta test with V.I.P. VOTING PRIVILEGES - help us make final-stage design choices! PLUS the official team History Fighter T-SHIRT and you will be listed as Agent Elite in the game credits.

:: The Asset :: All digital rewards PLUS the limited DECK OF CARDS and the T-SHIRT (above) PLUS access to our Beta test with V.I.P. VOTING PRIVILEGES and be listed as an Agent Commander in the game credits.
:: The Hero :: You'll get all rewards from the previous tier plus $50 in-store credit when the game goes live! You will be listed as an Agency Founder in the game credits.

:: The Legend :: You'll get all physical and digital rewards offered in previous tiers PLUS a 30 minute phone call or online chat with the game design team to voice your suggestions directly, and you will be listed as an Agent Legend in the game credits.

:: The Director :: WE PUT YOU IN THE GAME :: You'll get all physical and digital rewards offered in previous tiers PLUS a phone call or online chat with the game\u2019s creators PLUS we will create special game art after your likeness that will appear in the game when it goes live, and you will be listed as a Agency Director in the game credits.

:: The Overlord :: You'll get all physical and digital rewards offered in previous tiers PLUS you will get to design a set of cards (hero, minion, and relic) with us, and we will tailor these according to your wishes within the boundaries of our game universe! The design team will write and record a special song for you, and you will appear listed as a Supreme Overlord in the game credits.
